    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been updated with a high-flow water pump. While the finish shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally linear. A true analog masterpiece for the technical enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
